  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cool shit game made by a college student developer!</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215100/extras/dd4971b18e4bf6417bd5a93544a1d25e.avif?t=1685533214\" width=374 height=448 /></span><br><br><br>Avoid various traps and solve puzzles to help Balloon Man propose to the princess!<br><br>There are traps, puzzles, and unique bosses to confuse players!<br><br>There are stages with various concepts such as platforms, boss battles, chases, puzzles, and time machines.<br><br>Challenge yourself to speedrun and compete with people all over the world!!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cool shit game made by a college student developer!</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215100/extras/dd4971b18e4bf6417bd5a93544a1d25e.avif?t=1685533214\" width=374 height=448 /></span><br><br><br>Avoid various traps and solve puzzles to help Balloon Man propose to the princess!<br><br>There are traps, puzzles, and unique bosses to confuse players!<br><br>There are stages with various concepts such as platforms, boss battles, chases, puzzles, and time machines.<br><br>Challenge yourself to speedrun and compete with people all over the world!!",
